HEADWORD: Infrigidation
<hw>In*frig`i*da"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>infrigidatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of chilling or causing to
become cold; a chilling; coldness; congelation.</def>
